          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-09-03T21:35:15Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Block Arms to Iran Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill declares that, of the amounts appropriated or otherwise made available for the Department of State for &quot;Contributions to International Organizations&quot; and available for contributions to the United Nations, 20% may not be obligated or expended for that purpose if the arms embargo on Iran pursuant to Security Council Resolutions 1747 and 1929 is lifted, reduced, or otherwise eased.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-07-23T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
